snippet.title: F4 x MAYDAY五月天 [ 流星雨 Meteor Rain ] 5525版 Official Stage Video
snippet.description:
一場橫跨24年的青春盛宴
一首〈流星雨〉喚醒全亞洲的共同記憶
​
華語最強傳奇男團 —— F4
亞洲第一搖滾天團 —— 五月天 
神級合體，震撼降臨臺北大巨蛋
重啟《流星花園》席捲全亞洲的青春風暴
​
陪你去看流星雨，
陪你一起把奇蹟變現場
讓不可能在此刻發生！

／

♛ F4
華語第一傳奇男團，橫掃亞洲的青春現象級符號
朱孝天、言承旭、吳建豪、周渝民
以《流星花園》紅遍全亞洲，成名於世，更登上《富比士》，接受《CNN》專訪
被譽為「亞洲之光」的國際級偶像傳奇！
​
♛ MAYDAY 五月天
全亞洲最具代表性的搖滾天團，世代共鳴的象徵
阿信（Vocal)、怪獸（Guitar）、石頭（Guitar）、瑪莎（Bass）、冠佑（Drum）
巡演足跡遍及亞洲、美洲、歐洲與澳洲
征服全球多座指標性舞台，將華語搖滾刻進世界音樂版圖
美國《華盛頓郵報》盛讚為「華人披頭四」
亞洲媒體一致推崇的——「演唱會之王」！

​
／
​
MAYDAY #5525 LIVE TOUR
五月天 [ 回到那一天 ] 25週年巡迴演唱會
​
一生必看一場五月天！
🏆 橫掃 8 項國際舞台設計大獎
🏆 15,640 片 16K 巨型球體 LED，震撼視覺極限
🏆 斥資 2,600 萬美金，締造全感官極致舞台
🏆 螢光棒智慧連控燈效，共創沉浸式萬人圖騰秀
​
91場巡演，380萬人次熱血共鳴
雙主題、雙體驗，全方位升級感官震撼
2025盛夏，五月天即將締造北京鳥巢42場新紀錄
寫下華語樂壇前所未見、最傳奇的一頁！
​

#F4 #五月天 #MAYDAY
#MAYDAY5525LIVETOUR
#Concert #LiveTour

-

snippet.description:

She also puts different varieties of eggs to the test to investigate what’s really inside each egg and heads to cooking school to find out what the most nutritious ways to cook eggs could be. Are the most expensive eggs really all they’re cracked up to be?

snippet.title: Should You Always Press The Handbrake Button?
snippet.description:
Should you always push the handbrake button? People say don’t yank the hand brake without pushing the button. Let’s pull back the covers on this  myth. When you pull up on the hand brake, this pulls on a cable. This cable forces pressure to be applied to the rear brake pads, locking the wheel. The hand brake uses a ratcheting mechanism, so as you pull it up, the pawl clicks along the gear teeth until you stop pulling, where it’s held in pace by the nearest gear tooth. The button is simply there to release the pawl away from the gear, so you can disengage the parking brake. So it’s two robust metal parts, with very little speed between them, and thus negligible friction and wear generated. But to be safe, I stopped using my car entirely and now just walk, so that my parking brake doesn’t wear out.
